data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home, nestled in the serene North Springs subdivision, at the heart of Northeast Columbia. This charming property offers a wealth of features that cater to your lifestyle and comfort. Key Features include: The thoughtfully designed floor plan includes formal living and dining areas, providing an ideal setting for hosting and celebrating upcoming holidays. On the main floor, you'll find the owner's suite, which boasts a newly renovated bathroom. It features dual vanities and a generously sized Roman-tiled shower, offering a spa-like experience. The second floor hosts two large bedrooms, each equipped with walk-in closets, ensuring ample storage space. Step into the large fenced-in Private Backyard Oasis, offering both privacy and a recently installed deck – a perfect spot for outdoor cookouts and relaxation. Additionally, enjoy the in-ground pool during the summertime, creating a private haven for refreshing swims. The North Springs subdivision enriches your lifestyle with a scenic lake for serene moments of reflection and enjoyment. Benefit from recent upgrades, including the owner's bathroom, back deck, pool pump, and energy-efficient double-hung windows, enhancing the property's value and energy efficiency. Both HVAC systems were installed in 2019, ensuring efficient climate control, while the young roof adds extra peace of mind. This home is strategically located, with proximity to shopping, downtown & interstates.
